WEBVTT

00:03.230 --> 00:05.629
Your father is gravely ill in Moscow.

00:05.630 --> 00:09.069
You are Count Bezukhov
now, my dear friend!

00:09.070 --> 00:12.549
'You're the most brilliant man
I know! You could do anything!'

00:12.550 --> 00:15.389
He's going off to the war and
sending me away to the country

00:15.390 --> 00:16.435
to have my baby all alone.

00:16.483 --> 00:17.923
No, please!!

00:18.883 --> 00:21.403
I just wanted to come and
see Natasha on her name day.

00:23.683 --> 00:26.683
I know I'm just the poor
relation and your mother

00:26.684 --> 00:29.682
- would never let him marry me.
- Anything's possible.

00:29.683 --> 00:31.002
And he does love you, I know it.

00:31.003 --> 00:33.482
Russia hasn't lost a war in 100 years.

00:33.483 --> 00:36.642
This monster, Bonaparte,
he's crossed into Austria now

00:36.643 --> 00:38.762
and who's to say that
Russia won't be next?

00:38.763 --> 00:42.082
- Don't put yourself in danger!
- Mamma, please don't fuss. I am a man now.

00:42.083 --> 00:44.962
I request permission to join
Prince Bagration in this action.

00:44.963 --> 00:47.643
If one quarter of them come
back tomorrow, I'll thank God.

00:53.523 --> 00:54.802
Has Papa spoken to you?

00:54.803 --> 00:55.882
What about?

00:55.883 --> 00:57.242
He wants to marry us both off.

00:57.243 --> 01:01.882
Pierre, Helene... congratulations!

01:01.883 --> 01:03.923
- What's happened?
- We're engaged!

